sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User prompt
    participant OC as OpenClaw skill<br/>(Kalshi Trader)
    participant TR as Inbound translator<br/>(NEW - Person 1)
    participant GW as gateway.handle_tool_call
    participant POL as policy engine
    participant KA as adapters/kalshi.py<br/>(NEW - Person 2)
    participant AU as audit store
    participant HUB as StreamHub
    participant DASH as Dashboard

    U->>OC: "buy 10 contracts on event X"
    OC->>TR: native tool-call payload
    Note over TR: translates to ToolCallRequest<br/>injects context.skill_id="kalshi-trader"
    TR->>GW: POST /v1/tool-call

    GW->>HUB: agent_state(status="seen")<br/>(NEW - first-touch fix)
    HUB-->>DASH: deputy appears on Wanted page

    GW->>POL: evaluate(skill_id, tool, args)
    alt skill_match fires
        POL-->>GW: deny / require_approval
    else passes
        POL-->>GW: allow
    end

    alt require_approval
        GW->>HUB: approval frame
        HUB-->>DASH: approval card appears
        DASH->>GW: POST /v1/approvals/{id} (human clicks)
        GW->>KA: dispatch
    else allow
        GW->>KA: dispatch
    end

    KA-->>GW: result
    GW->>AU: record audit
    GW->>HUB: audit frame
    HUB-->>DASH: ledger row appears live

    GW-->>TR: ToolCallResponse
    TR-->>OC: native shape
    OC-->>U: "I bought 10 contracts"
